I will fill in the sex preparation
information. This is a procedure to
retrieve information about the partner I
will have sex with from now on.

Afterwards, I will call the sex details using
variables. There are three variables to
be used.

803: Current: Number of times having sex
806: Current: Number of times giving
oral sex 809: Current: Number of times
having anal sex

Please consider this as a tool used to confirm
which hole the stick was inserted into.

If ejaculation occurs afterwards,
ejaculation processing will be
performed. There are six switches to be
used.

804: Sex: Vaginal creampie 807: Sex: Anal
creampie 805: Sex: External ejaculation
808: Sex: Oral creampie 806: Sex: Anal
creampie 809: Sex: External ejaculation

This is a confirmation of where ejaculation
occurred after the stick was inserted.

The feelings towards sex will be processed
using two variables.

821: Current: Pleasure value 822: Current:
Emotional addition value

The pleasure value will be processed only
with a positive (+) sign, while the
emotional addition value will be
inputted and processed as a positive (+)
if it is pleasant, and as a negative (-)
if it is unpleasant.
"I was raped and my virginity was taken."

The situation will be directly inputted
into variable 943: Sex Act Situation ID.

With that, the variables and switch inputs
for sex should be mostly complete.
Finally, if you execute Common Event 16:
Common Event After Erotic Event, various
details will be recorded in the Erotic
Stats.

If you are being violated by a background
character, please add to the respective
experience count. For unique characters
with names, there is a treatment where
the count is only incremented for the
first occurrence, so this measure is
unnecessary.
